name: Trogon, StableStudio, life after Apple, Google's problematic new TLDs & how to discuss programming languages (Changelog News #45)
summary: Will McGugan’s Trogon auto-generates friendly TUIs for your CLI apps, Stability AI’s official open source variant of DreamStudio, John Calhoun writes about life after 26 years programming at Apple, Google’s news TLDs could be a boon to scammers &amp; Pablo Meier documents a way to discuss programming languages.
